            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-69" n="69">I Ne'er Cou'd Endure my Talent to smother.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-70" n="70">I have told you one tale I'll tell you another.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-71" n="71">A Ioyner to fasten a Saint to a Nich,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-72" n="72">Made a large Auger·hole in y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Im\<hi rend="italics">add</hi>·a\ges breech.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-73" n="73">But finding \y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi>·<hi rend="italics">overwriting</hi>·a\ Statue to make no Complaint,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-74" n="74">He'd ne'er be Convinced it was a true Saint.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-75" n="75">When y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> true <hi rend="italics">Wood</hi> arrives as he will there's no doubt,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-76" n="76">For thats but a sham <hi rend="italics">Wood</hi> they carry about.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-77" n="77">What stuff he is made on you quickly shall find,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-78" n="78">If you make y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> same trial &amp; Bore him behind.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-79" n="79">I'll hold you a groat when you wimble his bum,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-80" n="80">He'll bellow as loud as y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Devil in a drum;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-81" n="81">From me I declare, you shall have no denial,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-82" n="82">There can be no \<hi rend="italics">add</hi>·harm in\ making \<hi rend="italics">add</hi>·a\ trial</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-83" n="83">And when to y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Ioy of my Heart he hath roar'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-172Y-line-84" n="84">You may show him about for a New growing board.</l>
